{"tid":508622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"校內只能說普通話     廣州仔唔識「盞鬼」「巴閉」","createTime":"2017-12-24T12:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T07:29:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e6dc3f6c161efcf0969a709a7890226c2e43e6b4","tid":508622,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:18:43.000Z","msg":"【普通話教學推行五十年】<br />\n【學生今時今日已不識廣東話俚語】<br />\n<br />\n上世紀50年代，廣東省教育部門把普通話教學列入中小學教育工作，加上改革開放後，愈來愈多人到廣東省做生意，令普通話更流通。至80年代，全省小學規定每周要有一課教普通話；90年代，規定要加強漢語拼音訓練。<br />\n<br />\n現時廣東全省的學校已完全過渡到用普通話教學。在2010年，廣州民間撐粵語行動中，有家長反映小學有不成文規定，若學生在課餘時間說廣東話，會被記名和扣分。<br />\n<br />\n在大環境下，小朋友即使會說粵語，但地道的俗語，例如「盞鬼」、「巴閉」已經統統不會說。<br />\n<br />\n#班細路真盞鬼<br />\n#自己語言自己撐<br />\n#一人一句廣東話俚語<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1589609271183553/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1589609271183553%2F&d=sje3%2B0DU1fnT6lzq94Tz7IzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=9b66ae77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1589609271183553/</a>"},{"pid":"7aed59510ead6ab031b38760a7a3271b3020a680","tid":508622,"uid":19762,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:20:28.000Z","msg":"負評係俾中華人民共和國嘅"},{"pid":"4491bd9af02222798eaec3a5b68edad9521532e9","tid":508622,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"你雷啦"},{"pid":"8e8b1fe53c48109dffb48729a0e5877e1da96aa8","tid":508622,"uid":70946,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:27:20.000Z","msg":"粵語好快可正名為香港語<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df05d62e78408a8f76169c108ff491c19ca12b31","tid":508622,"uid":105538,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:30:45.000Z","msg":"昨日廣州 今日香港"},{"pid":"cd89435bca2dde7e401bfd94c4f8c007791a46c6","tid":508622,"uid":45368,"like":8,"dislike":0,"s